00:40:30.799 --> 00:40:33.359
are confidential, so just thoughts about strategies

00:40:33.359 --> 00:40:35.600
or suggestions for demonstrating expertise

00:40:35.600 --> 00:40:38.260
without violating confidentiality.

00:40:40.559 --> 00:40:41.500
