00:41:03.480 --> 00:41:04.720
and then they're gonna nitpick with you

00:41:04.720 --> 00:41:09.399
over how much you need to mask the details of the analysis,

00:41:09.399 --> 00:41:12.600
and if they do say no, well,

00:41:12.600 --> 00:41:16.739
