00:41:18.440 --> 00:41:20.320
to solve a similar problem,

00:41:20.320 --> 00:41:22.440
and you can go in from the get-go saying,

00:41:22.440 --> 00:41:24.239
hey, I wanna showcase my work,

00:41:25.200 --> 00:41:28.799
or do an analysis on movies or sports

00:41:28.799 --> 00:41:29.640
