00:52:48.800 --> 00:52:50.520
The one that was told to me that was,

00:52:50.520 --> 00:52:52.280
so I was in the gaming industry at the time,

00:52:52.680 --> 00:52:53.839
making video games.

00:52:53.839 --> 00:52:55.359
I'm sure there are people on this call

00:52:55.359 --> 00:52:56.319
who work in healthcare,

00:52:56.319 --> 00:52:58.319
