00:53:00.760 --> 00:53:03.599
which is I adjusted an analysis.

00:53:03.599 --> 00:53:05.040
The results were awful.

00:53:05.040 --> 00:53:06.199
The product was going to die.

00:53:06.199 --> 00:53:08.119
We were going to have to pull the plug.

00:53:08.119 --> 00:53:11.160
I felt so responsible that I produced the analysis

00:53:11.160 --> 00:53:12.800
that was going to kill the product.

00:53:12.800 --> 00:53:15.479
And a friend of mine told me,

00:53:15.479 --> 00:53:17.599
it's just an effing video game.

00:53:17.599 --> 00:53:19.680
No lives are at stake.

00:53:19.680 --> 00:53:21.800
And I think sometimes,

00:53:21.800 --> 00:53:25.560
we devote so much of our waking lives to our analysis

00:53:25.560 --> 00:53:26.599
and understanding the data

00:53:26.599 --> 00:53:28.560
