00:53:28.560 --> 00:53:30.319
And again, this is not for the healthcare people.

00:53:30.319 --> 00:53:31.719
This is for everyone else.

00:53:31.719 --> 00:53:33.239
Lives are not at stake.

00:53:34.280 --> 00:53:35.239
Sorry, healthcare people,

00:53:35.239 --> 00:53:37.079
